query:
SELECT 
  pc.categoryId,
  c.name as category_name,
  COUNT(*) as product_count
FROM products p
INNER JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
LEFT JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE (
  p.name LIKE '%Vial%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%vial%'
)
GROUP BY pc.categoryId, c.name
ORDER BY product_count DESC;
